citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:45p on
02-AUG-18.
ACI Bartels contacted the licensee by phone. The licensee stated they were not available for inspection.
